  <summary date="2021-10-30T16:53:56Z" status="Introduced in House">Increasing Access to Osteoporosis Testing for Medicare Beneficiaries Act of 2021

This bill specifies that certain Medicare payment rules applicable to imaging services shall apply to dual-energy x-ray absorptiometry services used in bone mass scans beginning in 2022.

The Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services must establish national minimum payment amounts for such services.</summary>
